name: Pegasus Seiya
description:
He is the main protagonist in the Saint Seiya manga series.
Is one of the eighty-eight mythical warriors known as Saints who have served the Goddess Athena throughout the ages, protecting justice and peace on Earth.
Possesses superhuman strength and speed, two of the many extraordinary abilities the Saints draw from their guardian constellations and an inner essence called Cosmo.

#041 Saint Seiya Pack
